org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotML
Interface EngineSystem

All Superinterfaces:
ActuatorSystem, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, RoboticSystem, System
All Known Implementing Classes:
EngineSystemImpl
public interface EngineSystem
extends ActuatorSystem

A representation of the model object 'Engine System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Vehicle Traction
  • Max Engine Force
  • Max Breaking Force
  • Max Allowed Steering
  • Max Allowed Velocity
  • Gear ration

See Also:
RobotMLPackage.getEngineSystem()
